    "\n",
    "def logplot(x,y,t=\"\"):\n",
    "    \n",
    "\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))\n",
    "    plt.subplot(141)\n",
    "    plt.plot(x,y)\n",
    "    plt.title(\"x ; y\")\n",
    "    plt.subplot(142)\n",
    "    plt.plot(np.log(x),y)\n",
    "    plt.title(\"log-x ; y\")\n",
    "    plt.subplot(143)\n",
    "    plt.plot(x,np.log(y))\n",
    "    plt.title(\"x ; log-y\")\n",
    "    plt.subplot(144)\n",
    "    plt.plot(np.log(x),np.log(y))\n",
    "    plt.title(\"log-x ; log-y\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.suptitle(t)\n",
    "\n",
    "    return None\n",
